# Outputs

This folder stores the output files generated by the pothole detection system.

## Expected Outputs
- Images with detected potholes and bounding boxes.
- Processed videos showing real-time pothole detection.
- CSV files containing pothole details such as:
  - Detection confidence
  - Priority score
  - GPS coordinates (if available)
- Screenshots of the detection results.

## Sample Output

Output Image: `detected_output.jpg`

```
Detected Object : Pothole
Confidence      : 0.94
Priority Score  : 0.87
Status          : High Priority
```

> **Note:** Sample output files will be added after the model is trained and tested.
